main event: A UFO sighting was reported at Gillespie Field, San Diego, California on June 6, 1955.
interesting points: The sighting involved a round, white light traveling at a high speed in a straight line., The object was observed at an estimated altitude of 10,000 feet., The direction of travel was from SSW to NNE., The sighting lasted for 2-3 seconds., Four witnesses included Air Force personnel.
witness description: Air Force personnel including a Lieutenant Colonel and two Flight Sergeants.
